Deep Experience – High Quality
The senior leadership team of BPI Packaging has deep experience in the chemicals industry and in operations that combines to ensure high quality products and service to all our customers.
 






									Bobby Dunn								

									President								

Worked with Unocal and W.M. Barr for more than 20 years before starting the Memphis plant for BPI Packaging in the late 1990’s. He knows all of the chemical and packaging vendors, which helps when developing a product line or looking for that uniquely performing chemical for your formula.






									Scott Imorde								

									CFO								

Scott is the President of RBM Venture Company which serves as the single family office of R. Brad Martin.  Since 1995, Scott has overseen all of the financial, investment and business affairs of the Martin family.  As an experienced finance professional, he has broad knowledge across a variety of disciplines including marketable securities, hedge funds, commercial real estate, estate planning, risk management, tax planning, C&I lending and private banking.  In addition, Scott manages the Martin family’s interests in a portfolio of 10+ privately-held operating companies.
Email Scott 






									Greg Parker								

									Director of Operations								

Greg  is recognized as a subject matter expert with paint and coatings chemicals. He worked for 26 years at W.M. Barr in various quality and operations roles and another 6 years at EMCO, running the Mozel plant.






									John Dillon								

									SVP, Business Development & Marketing								

John has more than 40 years of business development, marketing, and operations experience gained at Standard Oil, Ashland and 3M / Meguiar's. With a strong customer centric focus, he develops extremely successful products and long-term customer relationships, delivering sustained service and quality value.
Email John 






									R. Brad Martin								

									RBM Ventures								

Great operating partners need great financial partners.  We have that with R. Brad Martin and RBM Ventures.







We ensure high quality products and service to all our customers.






